title: New South Austin 1 Bed Apartment
posting_body: Hop on the Violet Crown Trail to Zilker Park, greenbelt, and the wildflower center.
Also just across the street from Whole Foods.
Shop and eat at the nearby high-end retail shops, grocery stores and restaurants.
Get the job done in the WiFi work area with conference room and work stations.
Spend downtime in the clubroom and social spaces with TVs, full kitchen and gaming.
Make a splash in the resort style pool.
Spend quality outdoor time in the courtyard with private cabanas, fire pits, grilling, and an outdoor gaming area.
9' ceilings, wood-vinyl plank flooring, granite countertops, upscale stainless steel appliances, full-sized washer and dryers, and much more!
"I am a Realtor/apartment locator in the Austin area.
My services are 100% free, don’t hesitate to give me a call.
If you'd like to learn more about this property, or would like to review other available options, call/text or email me.
Also at Grackle Realty, if looking to buy, we focus on educating renters on how to become home owners.
Follow us on our Instagram to learn more!
*I strive to keep my postings up to date, but pricing and availability are both subject to change.*"
